http://cruisecontrolrb.thoughtworks.com/documentation

To install:
Download and unzip.  It's a Rails app.

NOTE: run these commands from the installed location.

To add your project:
$ ./cruise add &lt;app_name&gt; -u &lt;svn_url&gt; [--username &lt;your_user&gt; --password &lt;your_password&gt;]

To start daemon:
$ ./cruise start [-p &lt;port&gt;]

To view Dashboard:
After started, browse to http://localhost:3333.</pre></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="footer">Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/">Sinatra</a>,
